    <div class="review-card reveal"><div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div><div class="review-text">The Avatara tasting platter for two was an adventure in flavours. I particularly loved the saffron panna cotta — light, delicate, and absolutely stunning. This is not just a meal, it is an experience.</div><div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">M</div><div><div class="review-name">Meera Iyer</div><div class="review-date">November 2024</div><div class="review-source">TripAdvisor</div></div></div></div>
